<plot>During a boring session of a scientific council Mr. Radev, a reader at the University, decides to leave the urban civilization and start a new life. On the road, a mysterious automobile tire that takes him to a mountain village, completely forgotten by people, with only one inhabitant, overtakes him. They - the reader and the peasant, try to conform to each other. The magic of novelty slowly loses its charm. Only a miracle is able to save their closeness -and they find a map to a buried treasure.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?668630</url></doc>
